cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper discusses video processing for object detection and tracking in a maritime environment, which involves computer vision techniques and robotics. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for object detection and tracking, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of various techniques on a newly proposed dataset, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia).
